<div class="container mt-5">
    <h2 class="pb-4">Persönliche Alumni-Daten bearbeiten</h2>
    <div class="alert mb-2" id="alert" style="display: none" role="alert"></div>
    {% if alumniVerified %}
    <p>Bitte aktualisiere über dieses Formular deine aktuell bei uns gespeicherten Daten, damit wir dich weiterhin zielgerecht kontaktieren können.
    Wenn du deine Daten stattdessen komplett aus unserer Datenbank löschen möchtest, klicke bitte <a href="#" style="color: var(--bs-body-color)" id="buttonRequestDeleteData">hier</a>.</p>
    <div style="margin-top: 20px"></div>
    <form id="changeDataForm" action="#" method="post">
        <input type="hidden" value="{{ data.id }}" id="id" name="id" />
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="name" class="form-label">
                        <i class="bi bi-person"></i>&nbsp; Vor- und Nachname:
                    </label>
                    <div class="required-field-block">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" value="{{ data.name|raw }}" required>
                        <div class="required-icon">
                            <div class="text">*</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="email" class="form-label">
                        <i class="bi bi-envelope-at"></i>&nbsp; E-Mail-Adresse:
                    </label>
                    <div class="required-field-block">
                        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" value="{{ data.email }}" required>
                        <div class="required-icon">
                            <div class="text">*</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="birthday" class="form-label">
                        <i class="bi bi-calendar-date"></i>&nbsp; Geburtsdatum:
                    </label>
                    <div class="required-field-block">
                        <input type="date" class="form-control" id="birthday" name="birthday" min="{{ minBirthDate }}" max="{{ maxBirthDate }}" value="{{ data.birthday != '0000-00-00' ? data.birthday : '' }}">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="graduation_year" class="form-label">
                        <i class="bi bi-mortarboard"></i>&nbsp; Abiturjahrgang:
                    </label>
                    <div class="required-field-block">
                        <input type="number" class="form-control" id="graduation_year" name="graduation_year" min="1950" max="2100" value="{{ data.graduation_year != 0 ? data.graduation_year : '' }}">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="studies" class="form-label">
                <i class="bi bi-book"></i>&nbsp; Studium/Ausbildung:
            </label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="studies" name="studies" value="{{ data.studies|raw }}">
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="job" class="form-label">
                        <i class="bi bi-briefcase"></i>&nbsp; Beruf/Tätigkeit:
                    </label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="job" name="job" value="{{ data.job|raw }}">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="company" class="form-label">
                        <i class="bi bi-building"></i>&nbsp; Aktuelle:r Arbeitgeber:in:
                    </label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="company" name="company" value="{{ data.company|raw }}">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 14px"><span style="color: red">*</span> Pflichtfeld</p>
        <div style="margin-top: 30px"></div>
        <div class="form-check mb-3">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="transfer-privacy" name="transfer-privacy" {{ data.transfer_privacy == 1 ? 'checked' : '' }}>
            <label class="form-check-label" for="transfer-privacy">
                Ich stimme der Weitergabe meiner Daten insbesondere meiner E-Mail-Adresse an Schüler:innen zur Kontaktaufnahme zu. Meine Einwilligung kann ich jederzeit widerrufen.
            </label>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 20px"></div>
        <button type="submit" id="submit" name="submit" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="bi bi-save"></i> Speichern</button>
    </form>

        <!-- Delete Data Modal -->
        <div class="modal fade" id="deleteDataModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="deleteData_configLabel"
             aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable">
                <div class="modal-content">
                    <div class="modal-header">
                        <h1 class="modal-title fs-5" id="deleteData_configLabel">Persönliche Daten aus der Alumni-Datenbank löschen</h1>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-body">
                        <div id="alert" style="display: none" class="alert pb-2"></div>
                        <p>Schade, dass du gehen möchtest! <b>Bist du sicher, dass du deine Daten aus der Alumni-Datenbank
                                des Gymnasiums Melle löschen möchtest?</b> Dieser Vorgang kann nicht rückgängig gemacht werden.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="modal-footer">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col">
                                <button type="button" id="buttonDeleteData" class="btn btn-danger">Daten unwiderruflich löschen</button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-auto">
                                <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Abbrechen</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="container mt-5 justify-content-center align-items-center" style="max-width: 500px; display: flex">
        <div class="login-form" style="width: 100%; border: 0.5px solid #ccc; border-radius: 10px; padding: 40px">
            <h2>E-Mail-Verifizierung</h2>
            <div style="margin-top: 20px"></div>
            <p>Zum Ändern deiner Daten musst du deine Identität verifizieren. Bitte gib deine E-Mail-Adresse ein, mit der du in der Alumni-Datenbank registriert bist.</p>
            <div style="margin-top: 20px"></div>
            <form id="emailDataRequestForm" action="#" method="POST">
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="email" class="form-label">
                        <i class="bi bi-envelope-at"></i> E-Mail-Adresse:
                    </label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required>
                </div>
                <div style="margin-top: 20px;"></div>
                <button type="submit" id="submit" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Verifizierungscode senden <i class="bi bi-send-check"></i></button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
</div>

<div style="margin-top: 50px;"></div>
